description: Forward primer used to transfer 3V5 epitope tag into A/B vector with an HpaI cut site. Includes an annATG start sequence and A homology cloning tail.
Reverse primer used to transfer 3V5 epitope tag into A/B vector with a ZruI cut site. Includes a TAA stop codon and B homology cloning tail
Reverse primer used to transfer YFP from pWJ1863 into A/B vector with a ZruI cut site. Includes a TAA stop codon and B homology
